{"tid":2415303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★荃灣條崩嘴爛橋 終於用得返！","createTime":"2021-02-20T06:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T07:10:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32c490e8342c18f95a9034815afa16138e5eb7c3","tid":2415303,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210219/439487134424895488341890.jpeg/8n7SyOn8VmP2qJqt2Mx7B6vqKkctVu68Fri93ha4vd4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210219%2F439487134424895488341890.jpeg%2F8n7SyOn8VmP2qJqt2Mx7B6vqKkctVu68Fri93ha4vd4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=83926fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kwt/doc/2020_2023/tc/committee_meetings_doc/TTC/20290/2_D_2021.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkwt%2Fdoc%2F2020_2023%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2FTTC%2F20290%2F2_D_2021.pdf&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=157e1ea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kwt/doc/2020_2023/tc/committee_meetings_doc/TTC/20290/2_D_2021.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n方案提到的其中一項建議，包括擴建荃灣德士古道荃青交匯處「斷橋」，據知該道300米長的「斷橋」原屬八十年代政府舊有規劃的第二階段道路改善工程，以應付荃灣填海計劃後的交通需求，然而填海計劃其後因《保護海港條例》而取消，第三階段工程被無限期擱置，「斷橋」從此閒置26年，去年3月被申訴專員公署發表報告，批評錯失發展新道路的黃金時機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/589465/%E8%8D%83%E9%9D%92%E4%BA%A4%E5%8C%AF%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F-%E5%A1%9E%E7%88%86-%E5%80%92%E7%81%8C%E8%8D%83%E9%9D%92%E8%91%B5-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%B5%82%E6%A5%B5%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F589465%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E9%259D%2592%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%258C%25AF%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25